OL,6,F"Looking at the market, and what the
OL,7,Fcouncil has said, the chances of us
OL,8,Fgetting a four-bedroom house are slim
OL,9,Fto none."
OL,11,FThe family is among a rising number
OL,12,Fwho are finding themselves homeless in
OL,13,FScotland, according to new figures.
OL,15,FOver the course of the 2021 to 2026
OL,16,FParliament, rough sleeping has more
OL,17,Fthan doubled, overall homelessness has
OL,18,Fgone up nearly 20%, and the number of
OL,19,Fchildren in temporary accommodation
OL,20,Fhas gone up 26% - the highest level
OL,21,Fsince records began.
