OL,6,FPaula was one of those people placed
OL,7,Fin a homeless hotel last year, which
OL,8,Fshe claimed was filled with drugs,
OL,9,Fviolence and sex work.
OL,11,FShe felt so unsafe that she chose to
OL,12,Fsleep rough in a Glasgow park for
OL,13,Fnearly four months instead of living
OL,14,Fin one of the hotels.
OL,16,FShe told ITV News: "As strange as it
OL,17,Fsounds, I was actually happier here
OL,18,Fthan I was in accommodation. The drug
OL,19,Fsituation, folk coming to your door,
OL,20,Fstuff you don't need when you're going
OL,21,Fthrough hell.
