OL,6,FThe charity says that a failure to
OL,7,Fprioritise fixing Scotland's broken
OL,8,Fand biased housing system will lead to
OL,9,Frising homelessness and further cuts
OL,10,Fto local services unless the next
OL,11,FScottish Government act.
OL,13,FShelter Scotland Director, Alison
OL,14,FWatson says: "We welcomed the intent
OL,15,Fbehind the First Minister's plan for a
OL,16,Fnational housing agency last week. But
OL,17,Fintent alone won't build homes.
OL,18,FWithout the funding to match the
OL,19,Fambition, homelessness will only rise.
OL,20,FAnd we need the new agency to deliver
OL,21,Ffor the people waiting for a home.
